{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjU1_0019","text":"只可追憶到 想追追不到","structure":{"line_index":19,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["回憶","失去","無奈"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["追憶","追不到"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,9,3,3,4,9,3,3,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zi2","ho2","zeoi1","jik1","dou3","soeng2","zeoi1","zeoi1","bat1","dou3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"只","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"可","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"追憶","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"到","pos":"PART"},{"text":"想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"追","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"追","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不到","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"表達對逝去時光的追憶，但已無法挽回，充滿無奈。"},"source":{"title":"夕陽無限好","artists":["陳奕迅"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_255","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjU1_0018","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjU1_0020","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjU1_0020","text":"好風景多的是 夕陽平常事","structure":{"line_index":20,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["人生","時間","平常"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["風景","夕陽","平常事"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,3,9,3,3,2,2,0,0,0,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["hou2","fung1","ging2","do1","dik1","si6","zik6","joeng4","ping4","soeng4","si6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"好","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"風景","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"多","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"夕陽","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"平常事","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"看似豁達地表示美好的事物很多，夕陽只是其中平常的一種。"},"source":{"title":"夕陽無限好","artists":["陳奕迅"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_255","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjU1_0019","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjU1_0021","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjU1_0021","text":"然而每天眼見的 永遠不相似","structure":{"line_index":21,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["時間","變化","獨特"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["每天","永遠","不相似"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,5,3,5,4,3,5,5,3,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jin4","ji4","mui5","tin1","ngaan5","gin3","dik1","wing5","jyun5","bat1","ci5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"然而","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"每天","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"眼見","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"永遠","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"相似","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"然而，卻指出每天的景象都是獨一無二且不斷變化的，暗示時間的流逝。"},"source":{"title":"夕陽無限好","artists":["陳奕迅"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_255","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjU1_0020","next_line_id":null,"paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
